{"tid":1224887,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大家關注下情緒健康","createTime":"2019-06-15T05:22:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T15:14:58.000Z","uid":207470,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e66f2ea48f16135b0a7ee80b5c26ae538c059979","tid":1224887,"uid":207470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:22:41.000Z","msg":"相信大家過去一星期情緒一定好差<br />\n出面打完仗， 屋企又另一個戰場<br />\n如果你一家人同一個立場都還好<br />\n但我好肯定有更多仔女同父母意見立場不一<br />\n今次一定好多家庭關係撕裂<br />\n<br />\n各位戰友隨咗照顧自己人生安全<br />\n都要照顧自己嘅情緒健康<br />\n給予自己充足睡眠、休息<br />\n可行情況下，落街跑個步、聽聽音樂<br />\n調節下自己身心<br />\n<br />\n一旦患上情緒病、創傷後遺症等，<br />\n個病跟足你一世。<br />\n<strong>唔好睇小情緒病，嚴重一樣可以攞你命</strong><br />\n<br />\n最後， 抖足精神， 聽日 616 一齊百萬上街遊行"},{"pid":"4432d49c32bbb87286bf4cf21b1081e743d16f27","tid":1224887,"uid":199631,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:38:07.000Z","msg":"俾啲<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">長輩圖</span>佢地嘆下啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvApfeS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvApfeS.png&h=9c1d414f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1woREG3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1woREG3.png&h=6a4b02f0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ss3x8Ay.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSs3x8Ay.png&h=52f34abb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7035765107a8a4bca1b25acd4e9d6eee48587bd8","tid":1224887,"uid":207470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:35:37.000Z","msg":"推推<br />\n有巴打出事喇。"},{"pid":"b30ec5ae57e7d232d0d37b9e51289cae3b956266","tid":1224887,"uid":207470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:59:40.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"3a5af5996faaa6b1de36a532734ae9f2b79ec0cf","tid":1224887,"uid":185092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:04:02.000Z","msg":"Copy返之前個留言<br />\n你經歷過咁大型事件有咁嘅情緒同生理反應係正常 你可以試下同人講下感受或上嚟連登講 如果你想一啲情緒輔導可以搵紅十字會熱線 <br />\n但如果過了一至兩星期仍出現如失眠 驚恐 冇胃口 影響日常生活 可以搵臨床心理學家或精神科醫生查詢"},{"pid":"ad5013385a72417cfbfac1276e776dc5024bb4a0","tid":1224887,"uid":192851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:06:12.000Z","msg":"大家可以入去望下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1273176672840778&amp;id=297450853746703\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1273176672840778%26id%3D297450853746703&d=MAn3riz0%2FQ%2FS8BFDrurXlX88up93QrsUiEJqOxYGoBw%3D&h=52e7a531\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1273176672840778&amp;id=297450853746703</a>"},{"pid":"0b5e70408ca9123390dcada02cb6f0a5836787a9","tid":1224887,"uid":76982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:06:17.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n情緒病真係會死人<br />\n我地唔可以再少任何一個巴打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ce040806a22ff1a3d189bf4edf5b64b9ce56d17","tid":1224887,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:08:12.000Z","msg":"呢個禮拜真係好嬲同好sad"},{"pid":"f303c7240ae08ddebb920cbbc379b50c5915cb1f","tid":1224887,"uid":188907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x9uERMC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx9uERMC.png&h=5f21c210&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《逃犯條例》修訂爭議越演越烈，周日及周三的反修例示威均演變警民衝突。災後心理輔導協會設立「救心熱線」，為受事件影響、對社會死心的市民提供心理支援服務，熱線為51815501。"},{"pid":"0e9502502d0d2d1218f6390569ff3da0dca88fb2","tid":1224887,"uid":151248,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:14:58.000Z","msg":"當你開始覺得頂唔順<br />\n請暫停睇手機睇新聞<br />\n如果你連唔睇一陣都已經有內疚既感覺<br />\n請正視你既情緒狀況<br />\n搵朋友傾下/向社工輔導員等求助<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：曾經有抑鬱<br />\n14年清場個排差啲搞到復發"}]}